18. a.      You are subject to 4 possible tiers of punishment.
18. b.       First (inofficial) offence you will a warning either verbally or via chat/direct message
18. b. I.     First offence You will be stripped of all your Gear, along an appropriate deduction of your Fame/SC Bank Account.
18. c.      Second offence You will be temporarily banned for the duration of 24 hours. (Realtime Value)
18. d.     Third offence You will be permanently banned from the Server
